quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif-lam-meem"
  2,2,"Thalika alkitabu larayba feehi hudan lilmuttaqeen"
  2,3,"Allatheena yu/minoona bilghaybiwayuqeemoona assalata wamimma razaqnahumyunfiqoon"
  2,4,"Wallatheena yu/minoona bimaonzila ilayka wama onzila min qablika wabil-akhiratihum yooqinoon"
  2,5,"Ola-ika AAala hudan minrabbihim waola-ika humu almuflihoon"